description:
Just Dance 2023 Edition also known as Just Dance is the 2023 edition to the franchise, and the first fully digital version. With the Just Dance + you can also play through a large amount of the past Just Dance library. Like other Just Dance games, you try to match the dancer's movements. Like other Just Dance games, it uses a star-based system, where if you score 10,000 points, you get 5 stars. If you score 11k, the stars are blue, and at 12k they turn purple. I'm playing the game until I get all five stars on all the main songs for the longplay, then I might do some of the dlc songs for fun. This is the Just Dance 2022 map of the 2010 song "Last Friday Night (T.G.I.F.)" by Katy Perry.
